<p source="SHANGBO.PINGWANGWENZHENGSHOU 6.34.1 (STRIPS 1-2) MACHENGYUAN 6: 256, 257 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0063_tls_001-1a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0063_tls_001-1a.1">競平王就鄭壽,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0063_tls_001-1a.2">訊之於宗廟,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0063_tls_001-1a.3">曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0063_tls_001-1a.4">‘禍敗陷動於楚邦,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0063_tls_001-1a.5">懼鬼神以為怒,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0063_tls_001-1a.6">使【1】先王無所歸,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0063_tls_001-1a.7">吾何改而可?’</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0063_tls_001-1a.8">鄭壽始不敢答.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.PINGWANGWENZHENGSHOU 6.34.2 (STRIPS 2-3) MACHENGYUAN 6: 257, 259 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0063_tls_001-2a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0063_tls_001-2a.1">王固猷之.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0063_tls_001-2a.2">答:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0063_tls_001-2a.3">“如毀新都戚陵,【2】臨陽,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0063_tls_001-2a.4">殺左尹宛, 少師無忌.”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0063_tls_001-2a.5">王曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0063_tls_001-2a.6">“不能.”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0063_tls_001-2a.7">鄭壽:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0063_tls_001-2a.8">“如不能,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0063_tls_001-2a.9">君王與楚邦懼難.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.PINGWANGWENZHENGSHOU 6.34.3 (STRIPS 3-5) MACHENGYUAN 6: 259-261 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0063_tls_001-3a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0063_tls_001-3a.1">鄭【3】壽告有疾,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0063_tls_001-3a.2">不事.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0063_tls_001-3a.3">陳(=明) 歲, 王復見鄭壽,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0063_tls_001-3a.4">鄭壽出,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0063_tls_001-3a.5">據路以須,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0063_tls_001-3a.6">王與之語少少,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0063_tls_001-3a.7">王笑【4】曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0063_tls_001-3a.8">“前冬言曰邦必喪我,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0063_tls_001-3a.9">及今何若?”</seg>
                </p>

</div>
